msgid ""
"Re-check existing translations using context-aware AI.\n"
"\n"
"Detects entries translated without app name/context\n"
"and fixes only those. Requires an LLM-based API.\n"
"\n"
"Compatible APIs:\n"
"OpenAI, Gemini, Groq, Mistral, OpenRouter, Grok\n"
"\n"
"Not compatible:\n"
"DeepL, LibreTranslate (no context support)"
msgstr ""
"Genover eksisterende oversættelser ved hjælp af kontekstbevidst AI.\n"
"\n"
"Registrerer poster oversat uden app-navn/kontekst\n"
"og retter kun disse. Kræver en LLM-baseret API.\n"
"\n"
"Kompatible API'er:\n"
"OpenAI, Gemini, Groq, Mistral, OpenRouter, Grok\n"
"\n"
"Ikke kompatible:\n"
"DeepL, LibreTranslate (ingen kontekstunderstøttelse)"
